# {{PROJECT_NAME}}

A real-time intelligence dashboard built with [monitor-forge](https://github.com/alohays/monitor-forge).

## Getting Started

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install

# Validate configuration
npm run validate

# Start development server
npm run dev
```

## Configuration

Edit `monitor-forge.config.json` to customize your dashboard, or use the CLI:

```bash
# Add a data source
npx tsx forge/bin/forge.ts source add rss --name my-feed --url https://example.com/rss --category news

# Add a panel
npx tsx forge/bin/forge.ts panel add news-feed --name my-panel --display-name "My Panel"

# Add a view
npx tsx forge/bin/forge.ts view add main --display-name "Main" --panels "my-panel" --default
```

## Deployment

```bash
# Build for production
npm run build

# Deploy to Vercel
npm run deploy
```

